    "We measured TMZ sensitivity of parental and RAD18 -/-LN18 cells in the presence and absence of methoxyamine (MeOX), a BER inhibitor 42, 43.",
    "As shown in Fig. 2f, RAD18 ablation led to TMZ sensitivity of LN18 cells only when we inhibited BER.",
    "Therefore, BER and RAD18 are redundant pathways for the repair of N 3 mA and N 7 mG lesions in MGMT-expressing cells.",
